  "description": "This package provides build-stage rpm automation to simplify the creation of Go language (golang) packages. It does not need to be included in the default build root: go-srpm-macros will pull it in for Go packages only.  \n\nSecurity Fix(es):  \n\n  * net/url: Incorrect parsing of IPv6 host literals in net/url (CVE-2026-25679)\n\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n",
